This paper deals with image processing using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques to solve these image processing tasks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also presents experimental results to demonstrate the effectiveness of the proposed technique, which could be considered as graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM) research.
